collection.name: Quantum Curated
collection.description: Digital Culture, Curated. Quantum is an NFT platform for artists and collectors to share their work with the world.

detail.name: Sift #55
detail.description:
A code-generated kinetic work, Sift creates an illusion of a shifting pattern. Each pixel is treated like a small entity of color, movement and feeling, softly blending into another one. 

Gradations ,lines. and radiating waves are not drawn, but emerge by virtue of a “color by number by time” method; each pixel is assigned a color modulus which oscillates at the same rate at a repeatable mathematical pattern. Color switching at a pixel level creates all the motion in Sift.  A high-energy sine wave causes the gritty texture of the fragments. 

Meticulously hand-tuned by the artist, the coloring math has been adjusted for each piece to produce the desired contrast and depth. Subdivisions of brightness and saturation were chosen for a softer feel, inviting the viewer to sift through and notice small emergent elements.

collection.description:
Airdrop coming on June 15th in partnership with Clinique!

All NFP holders will be eligible for an NFPet coming soon! (Free + Gas) 
You can also upgrade your pet to one of 11 different dog breeds with outfits, accessories and more! Deets in Discord.
Personalizations, Animations and more are available to show of your NFP! 
To update your OpenSea image go to https://nfp.daz3d.com/nfp/dashboard

Daz 3D’s debut NFT collection, Non-Fungible People (NFP), is a collection of 8,888 women and non-binary hyper-realistic 3D Avatars.  Each NFP comes with a fully rigged 3D model and a PFP rendered in breathtaking 3D.  Use your NFP for video calls, motion capture, game design, animation and more!

You can even upgrade your NFP with a new wearable from the [Champion x NFP Collection](https://opensea.io/collection/champion-x-non-fungible-people)

License: All NFP’s come with the Daz 3D interactive license found here: https://www.daz3d.com/eula
